{"tid":155443,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做過三個月速遞，你問我得閒就答","createTime":"2017-03-14T04:51:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-14T05:50:12.000Z","uid":82007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"74b52b0745dd40b65c281ead217effd2965b7da1","tid":155443,"uid":82007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T04:51:21.000Z","msg":"唔開公司名，制服紅黃兩隻色自己估<br />\n<br />\n盡量咩都答，反正做得個三個月應該冇人識我，唔驚自爆<br />\n<br />\n人工太低加上本身只係唸住做暑期工所以三個月後就走左"},{"pid":"d6c4b0edda12e10a2124bdb5832b8ac9b08aa19d","tid":155443,"uid":75507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T04:53:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔開公司名，制服紅黃兩隻色自己估<br />\n<br />\n盡量咩都答，反正做得個三個月應該冇人識我，唔驚自爆<br />\n<br />\n人工太低加上本身只係唸住做暑期工所以三個月後就走左</blockquote><br />\n做得果3個月就收皮，無人想知"},{"pid":"0367ca77e6e4adf2cfa8f2f261042f0ca919429b","tid":155443,"uid":82007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T04:56:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔開公司名，制服紅黃兩隻色自己估<br />\n<br />\n盡量咩都答，反正做得個三個月應該冇人識我，唔驚自爆<br />\n<br />\n人工太低加上本身只係唸住做暑期工所以三個月後就走左</blockquote><br />\n做得果3個月就收皮，無人想知</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做過三個月起碼都叫識得多過冇做過既人掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc4bc0109174cbc48bd65906404db6bdd6d4cd68","tid":155443,"uid":59632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T04:58:10.000Z","msg":"幾錢人工 辛唔辛苦"},{"pid":"38ad52fa6a6b89e5f9cc9f125a1cf55d5e1491f7","tid":155443,"uid":82007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T05:08:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾錢人工 辛唔辛苦</blockquote><br />\n佢同我計月薪，9000一個月<br />\n返一至五每日10個鐘，除返開時薪45<br />\not就50一個鐘<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得唔算辛苦，派重野有人幫手/車你到間野樓下<br />\n<br />\n加上好多時都係自己一個推住架車仔四圍走，好自由+可以蛇下王(個日少野做既話)"},{"pid":"a03ce5a52d4c13a755da5e6f9c389a56f0cbe5e6","tid":155443,"uid":82007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T05:19:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40f906003a609403a8020eaa5ebb6d832e568bd1","tid":155443,"uid":28163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T05:22:39.000Z","msg":"咁低 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f7fff631798c9e9bdc4a867ae87597af49d331f","tid":155443,"uid":82007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T05:29:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁低 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你指人工？<br />\n<br />\n係低既，隔離SF係我地兩倍有多，不過工作量就大好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74fc81fee11dad0d14c55a11688324703cb1e3f7","tid":155443,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T05:38:17.000Z","msg":"點解唔做順豐"},{"pid":"3df639c3f9932195886067aaea2456426aa50bfc","tid":155443,"uid":82007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T05:50:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔做順豐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔想咁辛苦，SF人工係高，但工作量極大，見過佢地一個推兩架D貨堆高過人頭既手推車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且我想做佢都未必請啦"}]}